<p>Some other festive favourites include a velvety Salted Caramel Brownie Liqueur, out-of-this-world Chocolate Orange Christmas Pudding, a Triple Chocolate Panettone of dreams and everybody's favourite - a Festive Colin the Caterpillar Cake, giving a new take on the Christmas Yule Log!</p>

